name: "The Fields of Grey Perceptions" Fuller
description:
"The Fields of Grey Perceptions" are 5 individualized 1/1 collage NFTs that run parallel depictions to the main NFT photographical series "The Fields of Grey". This is "The Fields of Grey Perceptions" Fuller

"The Fields of Grey" project is a visual chronicle narration of a community’s progression, but also one of personal growth and empowerment. "The Fields of Grey" leaves many open-ended interpretations up to the individual viewer. Project by DeadPanZoom
 
All Photos were taken August 2021 in Kapatagan, Philippines
